s:380:"<p>Understand <i>p</i> + <i>q</i> as the number located a distance |<i>q</i>| from <i>p</i>, in the positive or negative direction depending on whether <i>q</i> is positive or negative. Show that a number and its opposite have a sum of 0 (are additive inverses). Interpret sums of rational numbers by describing real-world contexts.</p><p><strong>Grade levels</strong><br />07</p>";